What sign are you?

14:12.000 --> 14:13.417
I'm an Aries.

14:13.500 --> 14:15.333
Yeah, but astrology's
complete junk science.

14:15.417 --> 14:17.083
Oh, my god, I'm an Aries, too!

14:17.166 --> 14:18.917
What are the odds?

14:19.000 --> 14:20.500
Uh, one in 12.

14:20.583 --> 14:22.750
VANESSA:
What up? What up?

14:22.834 --> 14:24.792
I'm at a drum circle
gettin' my groove on.

14:24.875 --> 14:26.542
Super hot out here.

14:26.625 --> 14:28.625
