were here.

14:28.709 --> 14:31.917
I'm sorry. How much longer
will we be enjoying this?

14:32.000 --> 14:33.125
Not much longer.

14:33.208 --> 14:36.083
Four, five hours maybe.
15 tops.

14:36.166 --> 14:38.291
Well, how about moving
to another spot?

14:38.375 --> 14:41.083
Hey, you don't own the beach,
one-percenter.

14:41.166 --> 14:43.083
A one-percenter? No, I'm...

14:43.166 --> 14:45.083
I'm a middle-class
social worker!

14:45.166 --> 14:48.500
