the other day. (chuckles)

14:48.583 --> 14:50.083
I...

14:50.166 --> 14:51.709
Who threw that?!

14:51.792 --> 14:53.667
Who the hell threw
that at my baby?!

15:02.542 --> 15:03.583
(gasps)

15:05.959 --> 15:07.250
Go throw your
drum in the ocean.

15:08.166 --> 15:09.166
Do it!

15:12.625 --> 15:15.166
What are you looking at,
Game of Thrones?

15:17.875 --> 15:20.750
Okay, baby, is it
sunscreen time again?

15:20.834 --> 15:22.000
Ooh.

15:22.083 --> 15:23.667
Yeah, I know.

15:23.750 --> 15:26.083
It's getting hot out here.

15:26.166 --> 15:28.250
You need a little
on your arms.

15:28.333 --> 15:31.000
Shyamalan.

15:31.083 --> 15:32.250
(laughter)

15:32.333 --> 15:34.166
You know, you girls are so cool
for models.

15:34.250 --> 15:36.166
You must have been very popular
in high school.

15:36.250 --> 15:38.959
No, I was
so awkward.
Really?

15:39.041 --> 15:39.959
Hey!

15:40.041 --> 15:41.333
Excuse me.

15:43.583 --> 15:45.291
What happened to your
pretty little lady friend?

15:45.375 --> 15:46.959
We had a really nice
conversation

15:47.041 --> 15:49.125
about the beef industry,
and then her and some guys

15:49.208 --> 15:50.291
started doing a ton of cocaine.

15:50.375 --> 15:52.125
