17:43.417 --> 17:45.250
What?!

17:45.333 --> 17:48.458
Hey, do you think Edie's
gone in the water yet?

17:48.542 --> 17:50.500
I'll see if Vanessa
posted any photos.

17:50.583 --> 17:52.792
